rComments: Baron runs a good class. He is well prepared for discussions and keeps things interesting. He's also extremely nice and willing to look over writing--even if it is not for class. When I took it, we did free writes every day, and it helped my writing immensely. His grading can seem a bit harsh.
Awesome teacher that simply gets it. You won't regret taking a class with him. He's an amazing writer as well.
